review_blob: This is an excellent beer, works great with a grilled lamb fillt. Or just as it is on a cold day when u are sitting infront of a bonfire.
one of my favourite APA atm. Citrus flavor. Really good to smoked meat, or grilled.
En helt okej l, lite fr mycket citrussmak fr min del. Snygg etikett och en klassisk flaska fr vrigt.
En fin blivande klassiker fr mig, passar bra till ljust ktt tycker jag. Bra blommighet.
I really enjoy that these kinds of lager is making a comeback in between all IPAs that is now out there. Lager has always been my favorite kind of beer and this one is perfect on a warm summer day.
